snippet.title: Bunny Girl Senpai ED: Fukashigi no Carte [ Lofi Remix ]
snippet.description:
Original Song from the Ending Theme to TV Anime "Bunny Girl Senpai" ("Rascal Does Not Dream of Bunny Girl Senpai", "Seishun Buta Yarou wa Bunny Girl Senpai no Yume wo Minai", "青春ブタ野郎はバニーガール先輩の夢を見ない") Titled "Fukashigi no Carte" ("不可思議のカルテ") originally written by Ameko Kodama and composed by Hidehiro Kawai featuring all the main girls in the series.

Now out on Spotify, Google Play, Apple Music, and more!
https://dj-jo.com/FukashigiLofi

BPM: 85
Genres: Lofi / Chill Hop / Electronic

---
Patreon: https://www.patreon.com/djjomusic
Support my Patreon for high quality mp3 downloads and uncompressed instrumentals!
---

Honestly, this song was already really chill so converting into a lofi song was a breeze!
Man, this song really hits me in the feels every time ahh

I really love this series and I hope there will be a 2nd season sometime in the future.

For the arrangement of this remix, I had a spontaneous idea to add guitar in the chorus and thank goodness I did! I really think it's fits the song very well! I hope you guys think so as well haha
Seeing how well the guitar worked with this remix, it gets me excited to use guitar more in future lofi songs!! I'll be sure to include it in some more projects!
Also, is it me or does this arrangement give you big city jazz vibes?

I am a bit behind scedule so I might not be able to make the Sunday deadline for my Centimeter remix. I'll let you guys know as the deadline gets closer!! Sorry! I've been a bit busy irl lately.

Until next time!

Also, thank you guys so much for the insane support of my kimi no sei lofi remix! It means so much to me!! :D

___
